   147→## Declaring _program_ variable
   149→Commander exports a global object which is convenient for quick programs.
   150→This is used in the examples in this README for brevity.
   151→
   152→```js
      →…
   177→## Options
   179→Options are defined with the `.option()` method, also serving as documentation for the options. Each option can have a short flag (single character) and a long name, separated by a comma, a space, or a vertical bar (`|`). To allow a wider range of short-ish flags than just single characters, you may also have two long options.
   180→
   181→```js
   182→program
